reviewText: I saw My Necklace - Myself when it first came out in the local Fallbrook California theater--the same town where the movie was made. There was no doubt in my mind that this film would eventually make it to the international market. It has won award after award on the independent film festival level; and again, I have no doubt this film will make a notable mark in film history. I would think this first public run of the film will be a collector's item in years to come.
